title: Honda Dio 125 scooter launched, price starts at Rs 83,400
description: According to a company statement, the Dio 125 boasts of features such as idling stop system, side stand indicator with engine inhibitor, multi-function switch for unlocking seat and opening external fuel lid, telescopic suspension with high 171 mm ground clearance.
